Mystery Case Files: Huntsville
Crime spree baffles Huntsville police! Do you have a keen eye for details? See if you can locate enough hidden clues to solve the crimes and become a Master Detective!

Mystery Case Files: Prime Suspects
The Queen&#039;s Hope Diamond has been stolen! It&#039;s up to you to search for clues throughout 22 levels, find the offending culprit, and recover the stolen gem.

Mystery Case Files: Ravenhearst
Discover the secrets behind the locked doors of the Ravenhearst Manor. Get ready for an all new Mystery Case Files adventure coming in mid-November.

Mystery Case Files: Madame Fate
A mysterious fortune teller has foreseen her own demise. Do you have what it takes to uncover the puzzling future and find the soul who seeks to kill Madame Fate?
